<div class="comment" id="comment-47771177">
  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/btown">btown</a> 18 hours ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">Are there any ways in Cloudflare to mitigate against this? If all sports matches basically mean &quot;our clients can&#x27;t access our Cloudflare backed app in Spain&quot; then it&#x27;s worse than fewer-nines; it&#x27;s a correlated event that could disrupt things like travel checkins, etc. - and it&#x27;s a hard pitch to say &quot;Cloudflare costs us money and it has no solution for its network putting our Spanish arrivals at risk.&quot;</div>
  
